# daisyUI quick guide
- CSS setup:
```css
@import "tailwindcss";
@plugin "daisyui";
```
- Use daisyUI classes + Tailwind utilities; avoid custom CSS.
- Prefer semantic colors (`bg-primary`, `text-base-content`).
- Themes via `data-theme` on `<html>` or `theme-controller` inputs.
- Only use valid daisyUI/Tailwind classes; keep layouts responsive.